    public static enum ColourDescriptor.ColourDescriptorType
extends Enum<ColourDescriptor.ColourDescriptorType>
    The different types of statistic available. This provides a convenient way of getting a single statistic, as the ColourDescriptor computes them all.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
